Usage: highlight_timing_report [-help] [-append] [-color_index <integer>]
                               [-file <string>] [-noarrow] {-path <string> | -all }

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-all                       # Higtlight all the path (bool, required)
-append                    # Append to current highlight (bool, optional)
-color_index <integer>     # specify the path color_index from 1 to 8.
                           # (int, optional, min=1, max=8)
-file <string>             # Specifies the file name. (string, optional)
-noarrow                   # Removes the highlighted arrow. (bool, optional)
-path <string>             # Specify the number of the path. (string, required)